Package: shannon
Type: Package
Title: Information-Theoretic Analysis of Genomic Data
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2025-06-19
Authors@R: c(person("Eylül", "Harputluoglu", email = "eyluelgoekce.harputluoglu@botinst.uzh.ch", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Computes Jensen-Shannon divergence and other information-theoretic quantities for genomic position files (GPFs). This package provides tools for analyzing DNA methylation diversity and other genomic features using Shannon entropy and related measures.
